gov.nasa.jpf.symbc.veritesting.ast.transformations.ssaToAst

Class CreateStaticRegions

  • java.lang.Object
    • gov.nasa.jpf.symbc.veritesting.ast.transformations.ssaToAst.CreateStaticRegions

  • public class CreateStaticRegions
extends java.lang.Object
    This class creates our structure IR from the WALA SSA form, this is basically done by decompiling DAGs within a Java program.

This is true for "top-level" Java if/then/else expressions, but if we wish to construct regions from within complex conditions, it no longer holds.
